data.description:
This property is move in ready.  Beautifully rehabbed home, with all new appliances including refrigerator, dishwasher, gas range and microwave. All appliances come with a Warranty.   All new hardwood floors throughout, new carpeted basement.  Bathrooms on first floor have been remodeled.  All new light fixtures and ceiling fans.  Roof is new as of January 2023, comes with transferrable Warranty.   Furnace was replaced in 2015 and Hot water heater in 2013. Back yard shed.  Perfect home for your family, must see before it's off the market!  Perfect location off Holmes Rd., close to shopping, dining and major highways.

Motivated Seller - Make offer.
